Package: PhyloTestESS
Title: Phylogenetic Subset Selection and Effective Information Diagnostics
Version: 0.2.0
Authors@R: c(
    person("Rui", "Huang", email = "huangr@example.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
  )
Description: Rebuilds the earlier PhyloSubset workflow as a package aligned
    to the June 2026 phylogenetic-dispersion manuscript. The package selects
    phylogenetically dispersed subsets and clustered contrast subsets,
    quantifies within-subset dependence with MeanOffCor, MaxOffCor, and
    MIESS, and provides prediction-metric-based ESS utilities for RMSE, MAE,
    and predictive R-squared under BM, lambda-transformed BM, OU, and
    early-burst covariance models.
License: GPL-3
Depends:
    R (>= 4.1.0)
Imports:
    ape,
    stats
Suggests:
    testthat (>= 3.0.0)
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
Config/testthat/edition: 3
RoxygenNote: 7.2.3
